A1

Kayar jo the
Woh shayar banay
Ab kya kya karein 
Yeh ishq mein

Bhagon mein dil ke, khilke in fizaon mein chaye ho

Main khud ter pau na 
Aankhon mein 

Shayar ki fitrat 
Mein hi doobna 
Main kya hi ladoon
Toofano se

Ishq mein tere 
Hain Faiz banay 
Arz kiya hai 
Humne bhi likha kuch tere baare mein hai

Haathon ko sambhalay mere haathon mein 
Kaise haathon ko sambhale mere haathon mein

D

Kya hi kahoon jo
Abhi bhi ankaha hai?

Na mahir na zahir

Haan jiya hai
